table.name: policy_by_group_number
table.viewSql: SELECT DISTINCT ON ((min(policy.id)), policy.group_number) min(policy.id) AS fk_policy_id, policy.group_number FROM policy GROUP BY policy.group_number ORDER BY (min(policy.id)), policy.group_number;

table.name: policy_date
table.viewSql: SELECT policy.id AS fk_policy_id, policy.date_start_effective AS start_date, COALESCE((COALESCE(policy.date_end_actual, policy.date_end_anticipated))::timestamp without time zone, (policy.date_start_effective + '1 mon'::interval)) AS end_date FROM policy;

table.name: policy_day_dates
table.viewSql: SELECT p.id AS fk_policy_id, dd.day_date FROM ((policy p JOIN policy_date pd ON ((pd.fk_policy_id = p.id))) JOIN day_date dd ON (((dd.day_date >= pd.start_date) AND (dd.day_date <= pd.end_date)))) ORDER BY dd.day_date;
